snippet.title: Leaked: alaplaya - Fantasy Tennis 2 - Trailer
snippet.description: Take a first look at the all new Fantasy Tennis season 2, a very lively mmo which is way more about using supernatural powers and fantastic skills than playing traditional tennis at all.
